data.description: Spacious contemporary family home. This home has a great floorplan with vaulted ceilings, and a large living & dining area. Wonderful, updated fireplace. Stylish light fixtures throughout. Iron Staircase railings. And a fantastic bonus room upstairs! Brightly renovated kitchen with built in hutch. Large and bright laundry room. There is a nice side porch off the garage (giving you three different outdoor seating areas!) The renovations throughout are a must see for this home. The beautiful back yard is large and has a great fire pit, and room for a garden too. This great home sits in the middle of Tulsa, close to lots of retail & restaurants!
